<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Elevate Your Website with a Modern Touch</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: white;
    }
    .email-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #34495e;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .email-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      color: #ecf0f1;
      font-size: 26px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .email-body {
      color: #bdc3c7;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .email-body h3 {
      color: #3498db;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .email-body p {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .email-footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #95a5a6;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9;
    }
    .pricing {
      background-color: #1abc9c;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .pricing h4 {
      color: #e74c3c;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Enhance Your Online Presence with a Modern Website</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Dear <%= clientName %>,</p>
      <p>I hope this message finds you well. I’m reaching out to offer an exciting opportunity to take your lodge’s online presence to the next level with a professionally designed, modern website.</p>

      <p>In today’s digital-first world, having an outdated website can be a barrier to attracting new guests. It’s time to transform your online image and capture more bookings by investing in a fresh, user-friendly design that reflects the quality and professionalism of your business.</p>

      <h3>Why Upgrade Your Website?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Boost Bookings:</strong> An intuitive and easy-to-navigate website with online booking options encourages direct bookings and eliminates reliance on third-party platforms.</li>
        <li><strong>Increase Visibility:</strong> A modern, responsive website improves your presence in search results, helping potential guests find you easily.</li>
        <li><strong>Showcase Your Property:</strong> High-quality images, an updated gallery, and client testimonials give guests a visual preview of your hospitality.</li>
        <li><strong>Build Trust:</strong> A polished, professional website conveys credibility and instills confidence in potential guests.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Discover How We Can Help:</h3>
      <p>Morudi Tech specializes in creating beautiful, functional websites tailored to the hospitality industry. To give you a better idea of the transformation we can achieve, take a look at a recent demo project we completed:</p>
      <p><a href="https://goldenfields-07nj.onrender.com/" class="cta-button" target="_blank">View Demo Website</a></p>

      <h3>Our Website Features Include:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Custom Design</strong> that reflects your brand identity</li>
        <li><strong>Integrated Booking System</strong> for seamless reservations</li>
        <li><strong>SEO Optimized</strong> to help you rank higher on Google</li>
        <li><strong>Responsive Design</strong> that looks great on any device</li>
        <li><strong>Easy-to-Update Content</strong> so you can make changes anytime</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Investment and Cost Breakdown:</h3>
      <div class="pricing">
        <p><strong>Custom Website Design and Development:</strong> <%= projectCost %> ZAR</p>
        <p><strong>SEO Optimization:</strong> Included</p>
        <p><strong>Ongoing Maintenance and Updates:</strong> Available upon request</p>
      </div>

      <h3>Let’s Chat About Your Project:</h3>
      <p>If you’re interested in upgrading your website, I’d love to discuss your goals and how we can build a website that brings more guests to your lodge. You can contact me directly or simply reply to this email.</p>

      <p>Reach me at:</p>
      <p><strong>Name:</strong> Kgotatso Nelson Mohlala<br>
         <strong>Phone:</strong> 082 962 0311<br>
         <strong>Email:</strong> moruditech@gmail.com</p>

      <p>I'm excited to help take your lodge’s online presence to new heights!</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br> Kgotatso Nelson Mohlala<br> <strong>Morudi Tech</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Morudi Tech. All rights reserved. <br>Visit us at: <a href="https://moruditech.onrender.com" target="_blank" style="color: #3498db;">moruditech.onrender.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
